data.description: Welcome to and discover the epitome of Southwest living at 9381 N Grasshopper Dr, Tucson, AZ 85742, nestled in the coveted NW side of Tucson. This charming residence spans 1,900 sqft! Embrace the spacious interior featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing an ideal layout for modern living. Enjoy this property with the savings off your electric bill with Solar Panels that have been paid off, and those hot summer days with your own private pool and spa! The location itself adds to the allure, situated in the vibrant NW side of Tucson, offering proximity to the outlet mall, scenic trails, parks, and a host of amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to call 9381 N Grasshopper Dr home!
